title: Mikalay Yanush
text:
Mikalay Yanush (; ; born 9 September 1984) is a <a href="Belarus">Belarus</a>ian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> coach and former player.
Career.
He was a <a href="Belarusian%20Premier%20League">Belarusian Premier League</a> top scorer in 2014 and 2015.
Yanush made his debut for the <a href="Belarus%20national%20football%20team">senior national side of his country</a> on 30 March 2015 in a <a href="friendly%20match">friendly match</a> against <a href="Gabon%20national%20football%20team">Gabon</a>.
Honours.
Shakhtyor Soligorsk
